      <title>韩国央行誓言在政治动荡中稳定市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/south-korea-s-central-bank-vows-to-stabilize-markets-amid-political-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自韩国立法者投票弹劾总统尹锡烈以来，韩国央行首次发表声明，誓言要稳定金融市场，并强调“不间断实施”关键财政和经济措施的重要性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/south-korea-s-central-bank-vows-to-stabilize-markets-amid-political-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国监管机构誓言稳定房地产和股市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/china-housing-regulator-sees-stabilization-signs-report-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在高层领导人会议呼吁加大刺激措施之后，中国监管机构承诺加大力度稳定房地产和股市，并实施更有效的财政政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/china-housing-regulator-sees-stabilization-signs-report-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 04:06:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>24 小时降息结束全球央行宽松政策年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/fed-interest-rates-24-hours-of-cuts-that-end-year-of-global-easing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年是通货膨胀率下降到足以让大多数发达经济体开始放松货币政策的一年，而随着美联储牵头的 24 小时连续决策，这一年即将结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/fed-interest-rates-24-hours-of-cuts-that-end-year-of-global-easing</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 14 Dec 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
